prompt:
Welcome! This is the first part of the experiment. It will last ~30 minutes. In this experiment, you are the head captain of a pirate ship traveling around the world to different islands. You will play a few different games during this experiment. Here is an overview of these games:


Part 1 (today)

1. Instructions, practice game, and quiz

2. Pick a pirate game on 6 different islands


Part 2 (1 day later)

3. Pick a pirate game and memory game

4. Where did I see this ship? game

5. Which pirate was the best? game


Part 3 (1 week later)

6. Memory game
